interofficeMemorandum.subject: SFA CO-LEVEL Q&A FOR TEST PRODUCT
interofficeMemorandum.body: Attached is the Q&A sheet public relations will use to respond to media inquiries concerning the co level of SFA test product. If you have any questions, please let me know.

instructionsForUse.whenTransmitting: Prepare in two copies and forward with material.
instructionsForUse.whenReceiving: Verify that material received is as described. Sign original copy and return to sender. Retain other copy for your files.
